org.mortbay.jetty.load.generator.listeners.responsetime

Class TimePerPathListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mortbay.jetty.load.generator.listeners.responsetime.TimePerPathListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, EventListener, LoadGenerator.BeginListener, LoadGenerator.EndListener, LoadGenerator.Listener, Resource.Listener, Resource.NodeListener

    public class TimePerPathListener
extends Object
implements Resource.NodeListener, LoadGenerator.EndListener, LoadGenerator.BeginListener, Serializable

    Use AtomicHistogram to tracker response/latency time per path

    Print out general statistics when stopping. To prevent that and only get the values simply use the constructor with false
